g to the streets with some new moves alongside fellow athletes.\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1127, \"end\": 1137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9999844491853288, \"rank\": 1.3497513094927096e-05, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1144, \"end\": 1160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Domonic_Bedggood\", \"score\": 0.9999999396868606, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Domonic Bedggood\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Domonic_Bedggood\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Domonic_Bedggood\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Footage\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1106}, {\"ngram\": \"the 36-year-old breaker\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1191}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1213}, {\"ngram\": \"some new moves\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1233}, {\"ngram\": \"fellow athletes\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Appearing to dance to Bruno Mars and Mark Ronson's \\\"Uptown Funk\\\", Gunn - who was named the top-ranked B-girl by the Australian Breaking Association in 2020 and 2021 - showcased some of her now-infamous shapes.\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1471, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1299, \"end\": 1310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Ronson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mark Ronson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Ronson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Ronson\"}, {\"begin\": 1328, \"end\": 1332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.999824500894579, \"rank\": 0.00010085765129156372, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1378, \"end